author: Rachel Clun
title: Former Olympian Grant Hackett in police custody on the Gold Coast
text:
Grant Hackett has been taken into police custody. Photo: Getty Images 
Footage shows the swimmer being driven in a police car into the watchhouse, at first covering his face but later showing his handcuffs to the television cameras. 
More to come... 7 News at 6pm: Former Olympian Grant Hackett arrested by police on the Gold Coast. Taken to Southport police watchhouse. #7News pic.twitter.com/nV29L60t6V â€” 7 News Gold Coast (@7NewsGoldCoast) February 15, 2017 Advertisement
